      <title>HEXO博客主题配置</title>
      <link href="/2021/10/15/Hexo/HexoTheme/"/>
      <url>/2021/10/15/Hexo/HexoTheme/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="config-yml-配置参数"><a href="#config-yml-配置参数" class="headerlink" title="_config.yml  配置参数"></a>_config.yml  配置参数</h1><p>官方配置说明文档<br> <a href="https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration">https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration</a></p><h2 id="网站资料"><a href="#网站资料" class="headerlink" title="网站资料"></a>网站资料</h2><h2 id="导航菜单"><a href="#导航菜单" class="headerlink" title="导航菜单"></a>导航菜单</h2><h2 id="插入本地图片"><a href="#插入本地图片" class="headerlink" title="插入本地图片"></a>插入本地图片</h2><h1 id="config-butterfly-yml-配置参数"><a href="#config-butterfly-yml-配置参数" class="headerlink" title="_config.butterfly.yml 配置参数"></a>_config.butterfly.yml 配置参数</h1><p>官方配置说明文档<br><a href="https://butterfly.js.org/">https://butterfly.js.org/</a></p><h2 id="社交图标-唤醒QQ对话"><a href="#社交图标-唤醒QQ对话" class="headerlink" title="社交图标 唤醒QQ对话"></a>社交图标 唤醒QQ对话</h2><p>如何唤起qq临时会话</p><h2 id="代码高亮"><a href="#代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="代码高亮"></a>代码高亮</h2><h2 id="文章页相关配置"><a href="#文章页相关配置" class="headerlink" title="文章页相关配置"></a>文章页相关配置</h2><h2 id="复製相关配置"><a href="#复製相关配置" class="headerlink" title="复製相关配置"></a>复製相关配置</h2><h2 id="美化页面显示"><a href="#美化页面显示" class="headerlink" title="美化页面显示"></a>美化页面显示</h2><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 美化页面显示</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">beautify:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">site</span> <span class="comment"># site/post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title-prefix-icon:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;\f0c1&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">title-prefix-icon-color:</span> <span class="string">&quot;#F47466&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
